sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>(Content Safety, Jailbreak,<br/>Sensitive Data, Topic)
    participant Models as Embedded ML Models<br/>(spaCy, Sentence Transformers,<br/>FastEmbed, NLTK)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>(Hallucination, Content Safety,<br/>Sensitive Data)
    participant Redis as Redis (Optional)<br/>6379/TCP
    participant OTel as OTel Collector (Optional)<br/>4317/4318 TCP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP :8000 (plaintext)<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    activate Server

    Server->>Redis: Load thread history (if thread_id)<br/>Redis protocol :6379
    Redis-->>Server: Previous messages

    Server->>InputRails: Apply input rails
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>Models: Content safety check (in-process)
    Models-->>InputRails: Safety score
    InputRails->>Models: Jailbreak detection (in-process)
    Models-->>InputRails: Jailbreak score
    InputRails->>Models: Sensitive data scan (in-process)<br/>(Presidio NER via spaCy)
    Models-->>InputRails: PII entities detected
    InputRails-->>Server: Rails result (pass/block)
    deactivate InputRails

    alt Input blocked by rails
        Server-->>Client: 200 OK (blocked message)<br/>HTTP :8000
    else Input passes rails
        Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Authorization: Bearer {forwarded_token}
        LLM-->>Server: Chat completion response

        Server->>OutputRails: Apply output rails
        activate OutputRails
        OutputRails->>Models: Hallucination check (in-process)
        Models-->>OutputRails: Hallucination score
        OutputRails->>Models: Content safety check (in-process)
        Models-->>OutputRails: Safety score
        OutputRails-->>Server: Rails result (pass/modify/block)
        deactivate OutputRails

        Server->>Redis: Save thread state<br/>Redis protocol :6379
        Server-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON or SSE stream)<br/>HTTP :8000
    end

    Server->>OTel: Export traces (async)<br/>OTLP gRPC :4317 or HTTP :4318<br/>GenAI semantic conventions

    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: Guardrail Checks (Fork-Specific, No LLM Call)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP :8000 (plaintext)<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    activate Server

    Server->>InputRails: Apply input rails only
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>Models: Run all configured checks (in-process)
    Models-->>InputRails: Check results
    InputRails-->>Server: Rail check results
    deactivate InputRails

    Server->>OutputRails: Apply output rails only
    activate OutputRails
    OutputRails->>Models: Run all configured checks (in-process)
    Models-->>OutputRails: Check results
    OutputRails-->>Server: Rail check results
    deactivate OutputRails

    Server-->>Client: 200 OK (NDJSON streaming)<br/>HTTP :8000<br/>Per-rail pass/fail results

    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: Model Listing (Proxy)

    Client->>Server: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTP :8000<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    Server->>LLM: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Authorization: Bearer {forwarded_token}
    LLM-->>Server: Models list
    Server-->>Client: 200 OK (Models list)<br/>HTTP :8000
